    "course_title": "DERIVATIVE SECURITIES - THEORY AND PRACTICE",
    "description": "Covers the pricing and uses of the most common derivative contracts including options, forward contracts, futures contracts, and exchange-traded funds (ETFs).  Also emphasizes a practical understanding of trading and management of portfolios of these contracts, and makes use of an online trading platform. Mathematical and statistical analyses are used throughout.",
